
ADDING LINEAR GRADIENT TO A TEXT:
-webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;



 ADDING SHADOW TO A PNG FILE:
     filter: drop-shadow(0px 19px 13px black);
   


ADDING ANIMATIONS TO THE COVER IMAGE (LAPTOP)

@keyframes drop{
    0%{
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-80px);
    }
    100%{
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0px);
    }
}